        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Transparency for Malign Chinese Investments in Global Port Infrastructure Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of the Director of National Intelligence to submit a report to Congress documenting all Chinese investment in port infrastructure globally since January 1, 2012, and the commercial and economic implications of such investments.</p>]]>
        </text>
